name: Leak & Rarung
description:
2038 x 2732 pixels

'Leak' was a human who is practicing black magic and have cannibalistic behavior. 
It is said that Leak is flying around try to find a pregnant woman in order to suck her baby's blood or a newborn child, to complete her magical skill. 

Rarung is Calonarang's most special student, because he is the only person who has ever matched Calonarang's supernatural powers, before Bhatari Durga cut his power.
